{"tid":489220,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"(唔好再嘈啦）Christopher Nolan 認為 DC 近年在拍攝電影上急於求成","createTime":"2017-12-04T12:48:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-06T18:36:22.000Z","uid":98659,"like":52,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"6f1afdbcd5bb466be5d6b8f724e075c9fd03a49b","tid":489220,"uid":98659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T12:48:10.000Z","msg":"被認為是 21 世紀最成功和最受好評的電影導演之一的 Christopher Nolan，最讓人認識的必然是他執導的蝙蝠俠三部曲，還有的便是《Inception》及《Interstellar》。然而最近 Christopher Nolan 在倫敦舉辦的 BAFTA 活動中亮相，便提及到他的蝙蝠俠三部曲各當前蝙蝠俠系列的分別何在。他指出他的蝙蝠俠三部曲推出的時間是很緩慢的，因此可以讓他有概念地開發及拍攝。接着他更補充他們用七年時間帶來了蝙蝠俠三部曲，是絕對享有特權和優勢才可以做得到；反之新的蝙蝠俠看似急於生產，未能慢功出細貨。<br />\n<br />\nThat&rsquo;s a privilege and a luxury that filmmakers aren&rsquo;t afforded anymore, I think it was the last time that anyone was able to say to a studio, &lsquo;I might do another one, but it will be four years.&rsquo; There&rsquo;s too much pressure on release schedules to let people do that now, but creatively it&rsquo;s a huge advantage. We had the privilege and advantage to develop as people and as storytellers and then bring the family back together.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/zh/2017/12/christopher-nolan-dark-knight-dc-extended-universe-difference\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhypebeast.com%2Fzh%2F2017%2F12%2Fchristopher-nolan-dark-knight-dc-extended-universe-difference&d=e00X04FWOkacxl1y7xrdRW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=292d7749\" target=\"_blank\">https://hypebeast.com/zh/2017/12/christopher-nolan-dark-knight-dc-extended-universe-difference</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好再嘈啦，神人nolan講得岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"259bc0ed79d20288e6c23fafabd2d6db84bdff7c","tid":489220,"uid":77180,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T12:50:59.000Z","msg":"Nolan煎左dc9一巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"655149f03cdfc931625069a09fcf6e46cdc4e80b","