l/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實咁撚顯淺嘅野係人都睇到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無論係咪dc fans都見到係擺明想追marvel進度<br />\n最後就搞成咁<br />\n死兜爛兜個班咪係dc9囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家nolan都出嚟講啦 有血性嘅以後罷睇nolan啦<br />\n唔撚好再講tdk trilogy 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"015ef6d6a1166636c2b8294ed5491b7c9346b4c5","tid":489220,"uid":94516,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-04T15:23:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>當初好似係佢推薦zack</blockquote><br />\n佢覺得DC無俾時間導演拍喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁公道d講<br />\n如果俾zack俾多一，套如mos2<br />\n雖然劇情都可能有個d眼高手低野，但打得爽爽快快，都還可以接受<br />\n情況唔會宜家咁慘"},{"pid":"8c94f43a933e6553be705253e00adabc0a70599b","tid":489220,"uid":75525,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T04:01:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>當初好似係佢推薦zack</blockquote><br />\n佢覺得DC無俾時間導演拍喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁公道d講<br />\n如果俾zack俾多一，套如mos2<br />\n雖然劇情都可能有個d眼高手低野，但打得爽爽快快，都還可以接受<br />\n情況唔會宜家咁慘</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMos 真係打得幾爽既"},{"pid":"c72c5e687bbbdfcc81087ca5de295dcd87c87f82","tid":489220,"uid":33190,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T04:13:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>當初好似係佢推薦zack</blockquote><br />\n佢覺得DC無俾時間導演拍喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁公道d講<br />\n如果俾zack俾多一，套如mos2<br />\n雖然劇情都可能有個d眼高手低野，但打得爽爽快快，都還可以接受<br />\n情況唔會宜家咁慘</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMos 真係打得幾爽既</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nmos劇情畫面動作都爽，其實佢2000年後好多戲都好，係唔應該咁快堆大堆頭<br />\n好多人都唔知你啲角色有咩能力，jl入到去，見到ww條繩，krypton呢啲字眼，好多觀眾都唔識，淨係哦一聲<br />\n<br />\nmos咪拍得好，ww都ok，你起碼比多一兩套普通戲，大家認識好你個世界，大眾先會投入到，宜家好多人仲處於摸索階段，套戲一入場仲要介紹幾個新角色比人知<br />\n單係mos，有冇睇過呢套戲既人對dc印象係完全唔同，因為你知道超人係個咩人"},{"pid":"ebf79a5779ae408f753b5639d4531a453daecf3a","tid":489220,"uid":86587,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T05:21:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當初好似係佢推薦zack</blockquote><br />\n路蘭帶起咗黑暗深度嘅風潮，DCEU又跟住東施效顰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Zack又係路蘭推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來搞彎DC嘅源頭就係路蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f456bd1796274be96ae48dfb1b552682da87bac3","tid":489220,"uid":31151,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T05:23:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>當初好似係佢推薦zack</blockquote><br />\n路蘭帶起咗黑暗深度嘅風潮，DCEU又跟住東施效顰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Zack又係路蘭推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來搞彎DC嘅源頭就係路蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔搞彎佢點顯得自己拍既三部曲神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4eec620b80d219c378b1cdb24fc0c1c57e4bf76c","tid":489220,"uid":96964,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T07:19:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>當初好似係佢推薦zack</blockquote><br />\n路蘭帶起咗黑暗深度嘅風潮，DCEU又跟住東施效顰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Zack又係路蘭推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來搞彎DC嘅源頭就係路蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果JL無搵joss轉風格 都可以話堅持有「深度」<br />\n<br />\n但而家一半一半 票房又差咪死<br />\n<br />\n利申：覺得JL唔錯"},{"pid":"53aa2df676f8713892d549777476153ba75258a9","tid":489220,"uid":33190,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T08:22:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>當初好似係佢推薦zack</blockquote><br />\n路蘭帶起咗黑暗深度嘅風潮，DCEU又跟住東施效顰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Zack又係路蘭推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來搞彎DC嘅源頭就係路蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果JL無搵joss轉風格 都可以話堅持有「深度」<br />\n<br />\n但而家一半一半 票房又差咪死<br />\n<br />\n利申：覺得JL唔錯</blockquote><br />\n前半部幾好睇，zack 個大戰好正<br />\n仲要以前廢狼大軍勁到連green lantern啲人都殺到，zeus果啲舊神都出齊，睇到joss果part<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無限弱化左咁，連ww+aqua 2個都可能打得贏佢，睇住佢如何比人sm十分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個個都唔知講咩好"},{"pid":"8e41b4e29ec91f198a1fbfa407d4ae93fdfe60f0","tid":489220,"uid":32063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T08:38:09.000Z","msg":"Nolan一句 全車靜晒"},{"pid":"5218b01303e1b632c378b0579b46868d4e557d11","tid":489220,"uid":98659,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T09:48:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Nolan一句 全車靜晒</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMarvel 狗幾串都唔夠串Nolan <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff6f5b0eed6aa5e541dba0c392680963b9a4592c","tid":489220,"uid":42283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T09:50:14.000Z","msg":"Nolan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39699c3d626956a5dfbbc4d5cce253df51c7f695","tid":489220,"uid":42283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T11:00:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>被認為是 21 世紀最成功和最受好評的電影導演之一的 Christopher Nolan，最讓人認識的必然是他執導的蝙蝠俠三部曲，還有的便是《Inception》及《Interstellar》。然而最近 Christopher Nolan 在倫敦舉辦的 BAFTA 活動中亮相，便提及到他的蝙蝠俠三部曲各當前蝙蝠俠系列的分別何在。他指出他的蝙蝠俠三部曲推出的時間是很緩慢的，因此可以讓他有概念地開發及拍攝。接着他更補充他們用七年時間帶來了蝙蝠俠三部曲，是絕對享有特權和優勢才可以做得到；反之新的蝙蝠俠看似急於生產，未能慢功出細貨。<br />\n<br />\nThat&rsquo;s a privilege and a luxury that filmmakers aren&rsquo;t afforded anymore, I think it was the last time that anyone was able to say to a studio, &lsquo;I might do another one, but it will be four years.&rsquo; There&rsquo;s too much pressure on release schedules to let people do that now, but creatively it&rsquo;s a huge advantage. We had the privilege and advantage to develop as people and as storytellers and then bring the family back together.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/zh/2017/12/christopher-nolan-dark-knight-dc-extended-universe-difference\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhypebeast.com%2Fzh%2F2017%2F12%2Fchristopher-nolan-dark-knight-dc-extended-universe-difference&d=e00X04FWOkacxl1y7xrdRW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=292d7749\" target=\"_blank\">https://hypebeast.com/zh/2017/12/christopher-nolan-dark-knight-dc-extended-universe-difference</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好再嘈啦，神人nolan講得岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n公開處刑最後一擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"217896a59020e9154fd3e02822bd88c377c2d6cd","tid":489220,"uid":54481,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T11:06:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://s1.ibtimes.com/sites/www.ibtimes.com/files/2017/11/19/aquaman-movie-release-date.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs1.ibtimes.com%2Fsites%2Fwww.ibtimes.com%2Ffiles%2F2017%2F11%2F19%2Faquaman-movie-release-date.jpg&h=6487516e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/d/d6/Tsangwordp1.jpg/revision/latest?cb=20071130025148\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2Fd%2Fd6%2FTsangwordp1.jpg%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20071130025148&h=30e6be5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.comicvine.com/uploads/original/2/20720/3425935-aquaman+sucks.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.comicvine.com%2Fuploads%2Foriginal%2F2%2F20720%2F3425935-aquaman%2Bsucks.gif&h=ce877b3d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"64a5d003f0b1aa6913484b8495e7ce5126184d10","tid":489220,"uid":42283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T11:17:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>被認為是 21 世紀最成功和最受好評的電影導演之一的 Christopher Nolan，最讓人認識的必然是他執導的蝙蝠俠三部曲，還有的便是《Inception》及《Interstellar》。然而最近 Christopher Nolan 在倫敦舉辦的 BAFTA 活動中亮相，便提及到他的蝙蝠俠三部曲各當前蝙蝠俠系列的分別何在。他指出他的蝙蝠俠三部曲推出的時間是很緩慢的，因此可以讓他有概念地開發及拍攝。接着他更補充他們用七年時間帶來了蝙蝠俠三部曲，是絕對享有特權和優勢才可以做得到；反之新的蝙蝠俠看似急於生產，未能慢功出細貨。<br />\n<br />\nThat&rsquo;s a privilege and a luxury that filmmakers aren&rsquo;t afforded anymore, I think it was the last time that anyone was able to say to a studio, &lsquo;I might do another one, but it will be four years.&rsquo; There&rsquo;s too much pressure on release schedules to let people do that now, but creatively it&rsquo;s a huge advantage. We had the privilege and advantage to develop as people and as storytellers and then bring the family back together.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hypebeast.com/zh/2017/12/christopher-nolan-dark-knight-dc-extended-universe-difference\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhypebeast.com%2Fzh%2F2017%2F12%2Fchristopher-nolan-dark-knight-dc-extended-universe-difference&d=e00X04FWOkacxl1y7xrdRW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=292d7749\" target=\"_blank\">https://hypebeast.com/zh/2017/12/christopher-nolan-dark-knight-dc-extended-universe-difference</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好再嘈啦，神人nolan講得岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n公開處刑最後一擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"318494db9bf4ec02225577c446f48dc747b7b6e6","tid":489220,"uid":81397,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T12:14:40.000Z","msg":"Antman 8年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f72ef3a50ac9a2183e7879d006b0f6c7f60ed1f7","tid":489220,"uid":34567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T00:18:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>當初好似係佢推薦zack</blockquote><br />\n路蘭帶起咗黑暗深度嘅風潮，DCEU又跟住東施效顰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Zack又係路蘭推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來搞彎DC嘅源頭就係路蘭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個人認為DC同Zack最好既作品係Watchmen，有畫面有劇情有深度。打後DC既電影真係拍得太急進，好多嘢都未準備好就推出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6480f4218672283dd103837b84685c8d40cf1442","tid":489220,"uid":4213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T00:23:35.000Z","msg":"DC狗 振作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}